{"tid":372441,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［昔日保家衛國 今日寒心維權］長沙退役解放軍維權集會影片流出","createTime":"2017-08-24T10:19:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-24T10:25:19.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f9b06ab0e16629e503753aeefbd37327cd658f06","tid":372441,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T10:19:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkcnews/videos/499526977057383/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkcnews%2Fvideos%2F499526977057383%2F&d=yfeJQzqMfDuJ5kb8qnbXrv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=bbb66a72\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkcnews/videos/499526977057383/</a><br />\n<br />\n請支持《眾新聞》，成為訂戶<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n據 自由亞洲電台報道，內地陝西、湖南、河南、四川多個地方的退役解放軍，八月中起，在多個城巿舉行維權活動，要求落實待遇。眾新聞收到讀者提供一段長2分45秒的影片，一批身穿迷彩服的退役解放軍，在湖南長沙巿政府前的台階上，拉起「強烈要求依法安置　拒絕強制自謀職業」，「昔日保衛祖國　今日寒心維權」橫額，又合唱《團結就是力量》等歌曲，並呼叫口號，但拍攝日期未詳。<br />\n<br />\n另據自由亞洲電台報道，200多名退役軍人，8月14日在陝西省委外冒雨舉行集會，要求老有所養，病有所醫。同一天，河南信陽亦有軍人到巿政府請願，副巿長出面與老兵對話，但老兵並無離去，當天下午，當局驅散請願老兵。<br />\n<br />\n今年2月，退伍老兵到北京中紀委及民政部等部門外請願。歷史學者章立凡當時接受 美國之音訪問時表示，退伍軍人不滿現狀，會成為中共統治的心腹大患。他指出，2月這次北京請願，有相對年輕的退伍老兵，他觀察到還有前軍官。"},{"pid":"4d7d99bffd4aae85ac33b7d55866c5105526447d","tid":372441,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T10:20:26.000Z","msg":"反了反了<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68096e27e993fef6a8f3dafde1720c0b7a277459","tid":372441,"uid":70786,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T10:22:04.000Z","msg":"搵現役解放軍殺撚晒佢地啦<br />\n想搞亂中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53c1eb4d1b24d5ea2bcd24a355e77f1832ad16d1","tid":372441,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T10:23:02.000Z","msg":"以前百萬裁軍都動搖唔到中央統治，何況而家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0beb85c48ea38ac0a72bddcb59a99f1ab581805","tid":372441,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T10:24:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以前百萬裁軍都動搖唔到中央統治，何況而家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/24/182447_72e2e7953cff92081e11ee8427e55cbe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F24%2F182447_72e2e7953cff92081e11ee8427e55cbe.jpg&h=b5fc3e9e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/24/182453_0d8749effeee8bdb8b250e8ca1e181e9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F24%2F182453_0d8749effeee8bdb8b250e8ca1e181e9.jpg&h=0f3a099e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c3a29459f73419d7b2108ba6be9142eb4022ad6a","tid":372441,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T10:25:19.000Z","msg":"解放軍仲賤撚過避孕套"}]}